## Docker

```bash
docker build -t flowlens .
docker run -p 5000:5000 flowlens
```

To pass environment variables:

```bash
docker run -p 5000:5000 \
  -e HF_TOKEN=hf_... \
  -e GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_... \
  flowlens
```

